WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:02.576
Nahisi sababu nimetoka Tanzania

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.280
nina wajibu wa kuwakaribisha
wote kwa mara nyingine.

00:00:06.360 --> 00:00:07.736
Asanteni kwa kuja.

00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.416
Kwanza kabisa, kabla hatujaanza,

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:10.936
wangapi wenu kwenye hadhira

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:13.720
wamekuwa kipindi cha nyuma
waathirika wa mdudu huyu hapa?

00:00:16.120 --> 00:00:19.216
Tunaomba msamaha kwa niaba ya
wakamata mbu wote.

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:21.056
(Kicheko)

00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:22.336
Mabibi na mabwana,

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:26.220
fikiria kuumwa na mbu saba wenye
maambukizi kila siku.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.400
Hizo ni umo 2,555 yenye maambukizi kila
mwaka.